linkedinDescription:
I am currently a 3rd-year undergraduate at the University of Oxford, interested in startups, ai for science, and artificial super-intelligence.

Previously, I won a gold medal at the International Olympiad on Astronomy and Astrophysics, received an Atlas Fellowship, and co-founded Qsium, the largest quantum youth network in the UK.
